<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weight Gain Plan (25-40 Underweight)</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Weight Gain Plan (25-40 Underweight)</h1>

        <h2>Diet Plan (Weekly Variation)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Omelette with cheese, whole wheat toast, and a banana smoothie</td>
                <td>Rice with lentils, grilled chicken, and sautéed vegetables</td>
                <td>Nuts, dried fruits, and a protein shake</td>
                <td>Baked salmon, mashed potatoes, and green beans</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Peanut butter toast with honey and a glass of full-fat milk</td>
                <td>Quinoa with grilled beef and steamed broccoli</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with honey and walnuts</td>
                <td>Pasta with chicken in white sauce and a mixed salad</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Scrambled eggs with avocado on whole wheat bread</td>
                <td>Brown rice with paneer and stir-fried bell peppers</td>
                <td>Handful of cashews and a protein smoothie</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with roasted sweet potatoes and spinach</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Chia seed pudding with almonds and a banana</td>
                <td>Chicken and vegetable stir-fry with quinoa</td>
                <td>Peanut butter with whole wheat crackers</td>
                <td>Turkey burger with whole wheat bun and roasted veggies</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Boiled eggs with whole wheat toast and fresh orange juice</td>
                <td>Salmon with lentils and sautéed greens</td>
                <td>Cottage cheese with flaxseeds</td>
                <td>Beef steak with mashed potatoes and asparagus</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Protein smoothie (banana, almond milk, oats, and protein powder)</td>
                <td>Chicken curry with brown rice and yogurt</td>
                <td>Handful of sunflower seeds and a protein bar</td>
                <td>Grilled shrimp with quinoa and a fresh salad</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Avocado toast with poached eggs</td>
                <td>Quinoa salad with chickpeas and grilled chicken</td>
                <td>Cottage cheese with walnuts and honey</td>
                <td>Baked chicken with roasted Brussels sprouts</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h2>Gym Routine (Muscle Growth & Strength)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Workout</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Upper Body Strength (Bench press, pull-ups, shoulder press, biceps curls)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Leg Day (Squats, deadlifts, lunges, calf raises)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Active Recovery (Yoga, stretching, light walking)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Full Body Workout (Deadlifts, push-ups, kettlebell swings, dips)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Functional Strength (Farmer's walks, sled push, battle ropes)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Core & Endurance (Planks, Russian twists, medicine ball slams, cycling)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Rest Day</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
